node.text:
THE VERTICAL DIET hard copy will be in Barnes & Noble Aug 10th and is now available for pre-order on Amazon. 
.
Co-authored by Damon McCune PhD, RDN, LD @drdamonmccune 
.
Damon and I have received over 100,000 DM’s, emails and messages from vertical diet users all over the world with Questions, comments, Kudo’s and yes, even some complaints, which we’ve used to continue to expand upon and update The Vertical Diet to help as many people as possible achieve their health and fitness goals. 
.
Victory Belt Publishing has done an outstanding job with the quality of this book and we’re excited to share it with you!!
.
Please be sure to let us know what you think. Thank you!!

.

When the Big Dog’s away, the cats will play!
.
2 sets of 500 yard 100lb sled drags. 
.
Damn, The air is thin here in Albuquerque 😓
.
@beattrainer 
@mr_nfp

node.text:
“ORGANIC” is a Marketing term. Sorry if that bursts some bubbles. 
.
Watch our YouTube interview with Food Science Babe @foodsciencebabe (Swipe 👉).
.
Repost @antidiet_dietitian 
・・・
☆ORGANIC FOOD ISN'T BETTER☆⁣⁣
By @antidiet_dietitian🥑⁣⁣
⁣⁣
This post may get some fire, but believe it or not this is my OBJECTIVE & NEUTRAL POSITION aiming to bring #evidence & shed light on #nutrition topics⁣⁣
⁣⁣
#Organicfoods aren't better for us & we probably can't tell the difference between them & non-organic #foods. There may be many ➕ things about #organicfarming, from ⬆️ #biodiversity on farms to movement away from monocultures, but producing foods that are healthier & #tastier simply isn't one of them🤷‍♀️⁣
⁣⁣
📍ORGANIC= NO PESTICIDES? It's been assumed that naturally occurring pesticides are somehow better for us & the #environment than those that have been created by men. Many #natural pesticides have been found to be potential/serious #health risks. Just because something is NATURAL doesn't make it non-toxic or SAFER. Both organic & #conventionalfarms vary widely in this respect. Some conventional farms use no pesticides. Some #organic farms spray their crops x2/month⁣🤷‍♀️⁣
⁣⁣
📍HEALTHIER?, Some people believe that by not using manufactured chemicals or #GMO farming produces ➕ #nutritiousfood. However, #science simply cannot find any evidence that organic foods are healthier than non-organic ones -& scientists have been comparing the 2 for over 50 years⁣⁣
⁣⁣
📍ENVIRONMENTALLY FRIENDLIER? while organic farming might be better for local environments on the small scale, they produce far ➖ food per unit land than conventional ones. Organic farms produce around 80% of what the same sized conventional farm produces(yields below 50% those of conventional farms!).⁣⁣
⁣⁣
⚠️A big problem here is the #myth when it comes to organic farming that you have to PICK A SIDE. Guess what? YOU DON'T🥳⁣
⁣
You can appreciate the upsides of rotating crops & how #GMOs may ⬆️ output & nutrition⁣⁣
⁣⁣
If you can & want to consume organic it's totally FINE if you are ok with paying extra. But CONVENTIONAL is great if you going for ➕ #VEGGIES & #FRUIT⁣ & that's what you can afford⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣

#Repost @kyle_cavnar with @make_repost
・・・
“The best diet is the one you’ll follow”. Excited to dive into this amazingly well put together hard copy of @theverticaldiet …just browsing through it and holy sh*t; my college text books were not this well written or in depth. Congrats to author and my new friend @drdamonmccune and all his hard work and research that went into this. To put the depth of credible information into perspective, the last 23 pages are just of citations from studies this diet is based off of 😬 (Est. over 500 studies!)

Another one bites the dust!
.
Less than 3,000 leg days left before I’m my pops age (he’s 90). 
.
I’ll be working on these elevator squats for a while. 
.
Went back to the @officialflexwheeler style quad workouts from 2009. 
.
Single leg extensions (mind muscle)
Leg press < 2 min rests (high intensity)
Substituted elevator squats for hack squats
Finish with banded step ups or lunges. 
.
The backside of the mountain may not be as glamorous but it’s a peaceful place ☮️
.
